{"title":"中国水兵","authors":["丁晓平"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":4,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国水兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丁晓平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是一个和水打交道的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像海水那样蓝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像礁那样扎实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血液流淌成国旗的颜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样的人自然是中国水兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他把故事挂在经纬线上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天就是他的宽脊梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海就是他的大胸怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走在海上如华表般巍峨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那动作那派头极潇洒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如中国堂堂正正的方块字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写在海上就是一座丰碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他种的庄稼就是台风和海浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他用中国那把锃亮的镰刀和斧头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收获"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种一海的风平浪静"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他偏爱蓝色和红色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像海水那样蓝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像国旗那样红"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}